title: Angela Rye Interview and more
itunes:title: Angela Rye Interview and more
description:
Today on the show we had our favorite political pundit Angela Rye come by to speak on Hurricane Harvey, Trump and even had some listeners call in to ask her questions. Also Charlamagne gave “Donkey of the Day” to Anne Coulter because she blamed Hurricane Harvey on lesbian mayor before climate change and Angela Yee helped some listeners out during “Ask Yee”.
